  "informal_statement": "For every natural number n, six times the sum of the first n squares equals n(n+1)(2n+1).",
  "informal_proof_idea": "Induction on n: peel the last term (k+1)^2 with Finset.sum_range_succ, distribute, apply the hypothesis, and ring closes the cubic identity.",
  "formal_statement_pp": "theorem sum_squares (n : ℕ) : (∑ i ∈ Finset.range (n + 1), i ^ 2) * 6 = n * (n + 1) * (2 * n + 1)",
